   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1️⃣ Prérequis système\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Python**: 3.10 ou supérieur (recommandé 3.12.10)\n",
    "- **UV**: Package manager moderne pour Python\n",
    "- **Ollama**: Pour les modèles LLM locaux\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2️⃣ Installation de UV (si non installé)\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Sur macOS/Linux:\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Sur Windows (PowerShell):\n",
    "```powershell\n",
    "powershell -ExecutionPolicy ByPass -c \"irm https://astral.sh/uv/install.ps1 | iex\"\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Vérifier l'installation:\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "uv --version\n",
    "python --version\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3️⃣ Installation des dépendances Python\n",
    "\n",
    "Exécutez cette commande dans votre terminal:\n",
    "\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "uv add langchain langchain-ollama langchain-core python-dotenv pydantic tavily-python langgraph\n",
    "```"
   ]
